Description
This is a metabolism model of Escherichia coli str. K-12 substr. MG1655 in SBML format.
iJR904
The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort. This file has been exported from the software COBRApy and further processed with a JSBML-based application.
This file has been produced by the Systems Biology Research Group and is currently hosted on BiGG knowledgebase and identified by: iJR904.
